-2JcCC_Yn0C&pg=PP1&dq=%22Marine+conservation+biology:+the+science+of+maintaining+the+sea%27s+biodiversity%22&ei=y_WqSujcB6S0NKC0_dcN#v=onepage&q=&f=false ''Marine conservation biology: the science of maintaining the sea's biodiversity''] Island Press. {{ISBN|978-1-55963-662-9}}\n* Duffy, J. Emmett (2008) [http://www.eoearth.org/article/Marine_biodiversity_and_food_security Marine biodiversity and food security] ''Encyclopedia of Earth''. Updated 25 July 2008.\n* {{cite journal |doi=10.1126/science.1173146 |pmid=19644114 |title=Rebuilding Global Fisheries |journal=Science |volume=325 |issue=5940 |pages=578\u2013585 |year=2009 |last1=Worm |first1=B. |last2=Hilborn |first2=R. |last3=Baum |first3=J. K. |last4=Branch |first4=T. A. |last5=Collie |first5=J. S. |last6=Costello |first6=C. |last7=Fogarty |first7=M. J. |last8=Fulton |first8=E. A. |last9=Hutchings |first9=J. A. |last10=Jennings |first10=S. |last11=Jensen |first11=O. P. |last12=Lotze |first12=H. K. |last13=Mace |first13=P. M. |last14=McClanahan |first14=T. R. |last15=Minto |first15=C. |last16=Palumbi |first16=S. R. |last17=Parma |first17=A. M. |last18=Ricard |first18=D. |last19=Rosenberg |first19=A. A. |last20=Watson |first20=R. |last21=Zeller |first21=D. |citeseerx=10.1.1.417.4642 }}\n* {{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.marpol.2007.11.003 |title=Positioning fisheries in a changing world |journal=Marine Policy |volume=32 |issue=4 |pages=630\u2013634 |year=2008 |last1=Grafton |first1=R. Quentin |last2=Hilborn |first2=Ray |last3=Ridgeway |first3=Lori |last4=Squires |first4=Dale |last5=Williams |first5=Meryl |last6=Garcia |first6=Serge |last7=Groves |first7=Theodore |last8=Joseph |first8=James |last9=Kelleher |first9=Kieran |last10=Kompas |first10=Tom |last11=Libecap |first11=Gary |last12=Lundin |first12=Carl Gustaf |last13=Makino |first13=Mitsutaku |last14=Matthiasson |first14=Thorolfur |last15=McLoughlin |first15=Richard |last16=Parma |first16=Ana |last17=Martin |first17=Gustavo San |last18=Satia |first18=Ben |last19